{{Infobox ethnic group | group = Cameroonians in France | image = | caption = | pop = '''51,625''' | popplace = [[Île-de-France]], [[Lille]], [[Roubaix]], [[Bordeaux]] | langs = [[Fang language|Fang]], [[Ewondo language|Ewondo]], [[French language|French]] | rels = [[Roman Catholicism]], [[Protestantism]], [[Islam]] | related = [[Black people in France]], [[Afro-French]] }}
'''Cameroonians in France''' consist of migrants from [[Cameroon]] and their descendants living and working in France.
==History== The first [[Cameroon]]ian immigrants in [[France]] came in the [[1970s]], like the [[Congolese people in France|Congolese]], some years after the first immigrant wave from [[Black Africa]] (Senegal Valley) in France.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.politique-africaine.com/numeros/pdf/067041.pdf|format=PDF|title=L'immigration africaine en France : regards des autres et repli sur soi |website=Politique-africaine.com|accessdate=7 November 2017}}</ref> But this immigration has speed up in the [[1980s]] (because of the social and economic crisis in [[Cameroon]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.memoireonline.com/01/09/1808/m_La-participation-des-diasporas-camerounaises-de-France-et-de-Grande-Bretagne--la-vie-politiqu1.html|title=La participation des diasporas camerounaises de France et de Grande-Bretagne à la vie politique nationale: émergence et consolidation de la citoyenneté à distance - Ruth Mireille Manga Edimo|website=Memoireonline.com|accessdate=7 November 2017}}</ref> to become one of the most populous group of immigrants from Black Africa in France.
==Notable people== * [[Samuel Umtiti]], professional footballer * [[Françoise Mbango Etone]], track and field athlete * [[Kylian Mbappé]], professional footballer * [[Gévrise Émane]], judoka * [[Véronique Mang]], track and field athlete * [[Francis Ngannou]], mixed martial artist * [[Dany Bill]], kickboxer * [[Teddy Tamgho]], track and field athlete * [[Calixthe Beyala]], writer * [[Emil Abossolo-Mbo]], actor * [[Vencelas Dabaya]], weightlifter * [[Serge Betsen]], rugby union player * [[Hassan N'Dam N'Jikam]], professional boxer * [[Antoinette Nana Djimou]], heptathlete, pentathlete * [[Cedric Doumbe]], kickboxer * [[Carlos Takam]], professional boxer * [[Gaëlle Nayo-Ketchanke]], weightlifter * Benoît Assou-Ekotto, professional footballer * [[Adolphe Teikeu]], professional footballer * [[Zacharie Noah]], former professional footballer * [[Yannick Noah]], singer and tennis player * [[Joakim Noah]], basketball player
