A '''program book''' is a printed schedule of meeting events, locations of function rooms, location of exhibitors, and other pertinent information pertaining to a [[convention (meeting)|convention]] or [[Meeting|conference]]. It is customary in many cases to sell advertising in program books to cover part of the costs of operation.

